headline: MergerWare collaborates with Mercer to Redefine M&A Deal Execution
summary: Mercer, a business of Marsh McLennan (NYSE: MMC) and a global leader in helping clients realize their investment objectives, shape the future of work and enhance health and retirement outcomes for their people, and MergerWare, a leading provider of digital M&A deal execution platforms, today announced a strategic alliance aimed at improving how organizations plan, manage, and execute mergers and acquisitions.
